snippet.title: Two Point Hospital: Close Encounters - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Put on those tin foil hats, Two Point Hospital takes a dive into the extra terrestrial unknown with the all new Close Encounters DLC! 

Including three new unusual hospitals set in different locations, 34 new illnesses (including 11 visual illnesses), three new cure rooms, as well as new challenges, features and of course, you get to see them aliens.
